16:31.550 --> 16:34.781
OH. WELL,
LET'S GETS SOME PRINTS.

16:34.820 --> 16:37.357
WE FIND OUR GOLFER,
WE FIND OUR KILLER.

16:41.300 --> 16:42.119
DID YOU FIND BILL POWER'S
NEXT OF KIN?

16:42.160 --> 16:43.320
