NOTIFICATIONS AT THE ACADEMY,

17:56.740 --> 17:58.560
AND I BREEZED
THROUGH IT.

17:58.610 --> 18:00.305
NOW I NEED TO GET
IN THE GAME FOR REAL.

18:00.340 --> 18:05.209
FINE, BUT YOU NEED TO BE CLEAR
AND TO THE POINT.

18:05.250 --> 18:08.344
MM-HMM.

18:08.380 --> 18:10.484
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
[ Muffled ] FUELING UP.

18:10.520 --> 18:14.650
SORRY. WHAT?
FUELING UP.

18:14.690 --> 18:16.681
[ COUGHING ]

18:22.300 --> 18:24.791
ARE YOU OKAY?
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

18:24.830 --> 18:27.469
NOW I HAVE A PEANUT STUCK
IN MY THROAT. [ COUGHS ]

18:27.500 --> 18:30.833
