19:07.780 --> 19:09.668
UH, MA'AM.
[ COUGHS ] MA'AM.

19:11.310 --> 19:12.948
NO, WHAT'S GOING ON?
I'M JUST NERVOUS.

19:12.980 --> 19:14.641
