HOW COULD THIS HAVE HAPPENED?

19:27.300 --> 19:28.790
HE WAS JUST AT WORK.

19:28.830 --> 19:30.661
WE'RE STILL
TRYING TO FIGURE THAT OUT.

19:30.700 --> 19:33.396
