MM-HMM.

19:41.440 --> 19:42.805
[ SIGHS ]

19:42.840 --> 19:44.979
WE JUST -- WE JUST HAD DINNER
TOGETHER LAST NIGHT.

19:45.010 --> 19:47.547
[ WATER RUNNING ]
HOW AM I SUPPOSED TO FEEL?

19:47.580 --> 19:50.686
[ WATER SHUTS OFF ]
I DON'T KNOW WHAT TO DO.

19:50.720 --> 19:53.211
WHAT DO I DO
WITH THIS STUFF?

19:53.260 --> 19:55.785
NOW COULD GRAB MRS. POWER
A GLASS OF WATER?

19:55.820 --> 19:59.426
