20:59.850 --> 21:01.351
UH, NICK'S BRINGING IN
MEGHAN KELLY,

21:01.390 --> 21:02.618
THE LAST CUSTOMER ON RECORD.

21:04.590 --> 21:05.682
FOR POSSESSION OF COCAINE.

21:05.730 --> 21:08.494
