21:19.670 --> 21:21.877
YOU SOLD SOME DVDs YESTERDAY
AT 5:17 pm.

21:21.910 --> 21:25.471
YES,
I SOLD MY STASH OF PORN...

21:25.510 --> 21:27.649
HOPING TO BUY IT BACK
LATER.

21:27.680 --> 21:29.648
DID YOU NOTICE ANYONE ELSE

21:29.680 --> 21:31.511
