ANYTHING UNUSUAL?
UNUSUAL HOW?

21:35.720 --> 21:37.859
UNUSUAL -- WAS ANYBODY
AGGRAVATED, ANGRY, UPSET?

21:37.890 --> 21:39.585
YEAH, ACTUALLY.

21:39.630 --> 21:41.996
