THE WHOLE DEATH-NOTE THING?

22:46.130 --> 22:48.018
OKAY, YOU REALIZE
THAT YOU'RE NOT SAVING ANY TIME

22:48.060 --> 22:49.698
BY CALLING IT A DEATH NOTE,
RIGHT?

22:49.730 --> 22:51.766
OKAY, BUT, NO --
JUST HOLD UP. HEY, TRACE.

22:51.800 --> 22:54.030
OH. HEY.

22:54.070 --> 22:57.562
WE GOT THOSE PRINTS IN
ON THE GOLF CLUB FROM FORENSICS.

22:57.610 --> 22:59.532
