40:51.680 --> 40:55.172
AND I KNOW
HE'S REINVENTED HIMSELF

40:55.220 --> 40:59.509
AND HE'S SAVING LIVES AND
RESCUING PUPPIES -- WHATEVER.

40:59.550 --> 41:06.251
BUT, UH, EVENTUALLY, LIFE WILL
THROW YOU A PILE OF LEMONS.

41:06.290 --> 41:09.123
AND, UH,
WHEN THAT DAY COMES

41:09.160 --> 41:11.993
[CLICKS TONGUE]
THERE'S NO LEMONADE,

41:12.030 --> 41:13.895
NOT WITH SAM.

